          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1Heat the oven to 450\u00b0F and arrange a rack in the middle. Place corn cobs on the oven rack and roast until knife tender and golden brown in spots, about 25 minutes. Remove to a cutting board until cool enough to handle, about 2 minutes, then slice kernels off the cobs."
        },
