          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2Add black-eyed peas, jalape\u00f1os, tomato, bell pepper, onion, and corn kernels to the bowl with the dressing and stir until well coated. Cover and refrigerate for at least 4 hours or overnight."
